Masa pak cik sakit.

1475
02:15:05,833 --> 02:15:07,291
Dalam filem pun ada.

1476
02:15:12,625 --> 02:15:14,000
Saya jumpa pita itu.

1477
02:15:15,791 --> 02:15:17,000
Di bilik pak cik.

1478
02:15:18,791 --> 02:15:20,250
Saya tengok.

1479
02:15:21,666 --> 02:15:23,375
