1491
02:16:15,041 --> 02:16:16,208
Pak cik dah tengok?

1492
02:16:29,375 --> 02:16:31,875
Saya ingat sesuatu. Betulkah ingatan saya?

1493
02:16:42,666 --> 02:16:44,666
Betulkah rakaman saya dah hilang?

