02:20:01,375 --> 02:20:03,750
<i>…sangat cantik, Saliha.</i>

1530
02:20:04,666 --> 02:20:07,458
<i>Oh, nenek. Nenek sangat baik.</i>

1531
02:20:08,333 --> 02:20:10,708
Nenek nak gambar pakai cermin mata.

1532
02:20:10,791 --> 02:20:13,291
