1544
02:21:03,500 --> 02:21:05,208
<i>Bukan nenek, mak akan pasang.</i>

1545
02:21:08,166 --> 02:21:11,166
<i>- Nenek tak boleh tidur.</i>
<i>- Bila?</i>

1546
02:21:11,750 --> 02:21:15,250
